    summary: '明朝第三位皇帝朱棣，迁都北京、派郑和下西洋、编纂《永乐大典》。',
    summaryEn: 'Third Ming emperor who moved the capital to Beijing, dispatched Zheng He\'s treasure fleets, and commissioned the Yongle Encyclopedia.',
    description: '朱棣是朱元璋第四子，封燕王镇守北平。建文帝削藩时他以「清君侧」为名发动靖难之役，四年后攻入南京夺取皇位。他的在位是明朝最具扩张性的时期——迁都北京、五次亲征漠北、派郑和七下西洋远达非洲东岸、编纂规模空前的《永乐大典》、修筑紫禁城。但他设立东厂开启了明代特务政治的先河，且靖难之役中屠杀建文旧臣的手段极为残酷。',
    descriptionEn: 'Zhu Di, fourth son of Zhu Yuanzhang, served as Prince of Yan at Beiping. When the Jianwen Emperor began stripping princely powers, Zhu Di launched the Jingnan (\'pacification\') Campaign and seized the throne after four years of civil war. His reign was Ming\'s most expansionist — moving the capital to Beijing, leading five personal campaigns into the steppe, dispatching Zheng He\'s seven voyages to East Africa, compiling the monumental Yongle Encyclopedia, and building the Forbidden City. But he also established the Eastern Depot secret police and massacred Jianwen loyalists with exceptional cruelty.',
    alternativeNames: ['朱棣', 'Zhu Di'],
    sourceIds: ['src-mingshi'],
