    summary: '弗拉维王朝开创者，结束四帝内乱之年，建造罗马斗兽场，以务实和幽默感著称。',
    summaryEn: 'Founder of the Flavian dynasty who ended the Year of the Four Emperors; builder of the Colosseum, known for pragmatism and wry humor.',
    description: '韦斯帕芗出身平民骑士阶层——这在罗马皇帝中非常罕见。尼禄死后罗马陷入「四帝之年」的混乱，他率领东部军团杀回罗马夺取政权。他以务实著称——开征公共厕所税（催生了「金钱不臭」的名言）、开始建造罗马斗兽场、平定犹太起义（其子提图斯摧毁了耶路撒冷圣殿）。他恢复了被尼禄耗尽的国家财政，临终还不忘调侃自己被神化的命运：「天哪，我想我正在变成神。」',
    descriptionEn: 'Vespasian came from the equestrian order — rare among emperors. During the \'Year of the Four Emperors\' after Nero\'s death, he marched his eastern legions on Rome and seized power. Notoriously practical, he taxed public toilets (giving us the phrase \'money doesn\'t stink\'), began the Colosseum, and crushed the Jewish Revolt (his son Titus destroyed the Jerusalem Temple). He restored the state finances Nero had drained, and on his deathbed, with characteristic wit, quipped: \'Dear me, I think I\'m becoming a god.\'',
